    """
    {
      "auto_resolve": false,
      "name": "test-metaalarm-to-update-1-updated",
      "patterns": null,
      "type": "complex"
    }
    """
    Then the response code should be 200
    Then the response body should contain:
    """
    {
      "_id": "test-metaalarm-to-update-1",
